
What to do to release Akunambol:

- Bump the version via CMake
- Tag a git version (git tag -s v<VERSION>)
- Get a tarball from git-archive, check and md5sum it
   git archive --format=tar --prefix=akunambol-VERSION/ vVERSION | gzip > akunambol-VERSION.tar.gz

- I said you must check your tarball
- Upload tag to gitorious
- Add a new version to bugzilla
- Write an announcement
  - Update the website
  - Send info to funambol and kdepim ML
  - Notify packagers

Optional:

- Write a blog entry
- Party :)

